caption:
Table 5. All of 
these landmark detectors share the same set of face bound-
ing boxes. In general, different landmark detectors do not 
make a huge performance difference compared to different 
features, and this implies that CNN features attain a certain 
level of spatial invariance. On the other hand, initial seed 

landmarks do help to largely improve face recognition per-
formance.
